task.summary: -Added XML parsing of Verkeerslicht -Added additional check if ->GetText is null to counter something like <baan></baan>
-Added attribute 'type' to class Voertuiggenerator -Added proper constructor/getters/setters for Voertuiggenerator -Added Voertuiggenerator XML parsing
-Added Bushalte class -Added XML parsing functionality for Bushalte
-Added Kruispunt class -Added XML parsing functionality to Kruispunt -XmlParser.cpp FINISHED
Aanpassingen van Raj aan de parser

-Added the Simulatie class that will end up outputting all required information regarding the simulation. -Added Car movement using mathematical formulas. -- Cars may not surpass eachother! -getParsedVoertuigen is now called by reference so that it can be used to modify the parsedVoertuigen in the simulation. -Added sortVoertuigen function to sort vectors of class Voertuig based on position (highest comes first). -Parsed vectors of class Voertuig are now automatically sorted to avoid conflict with the mathematical formulas
Alleen Raj - Alle testen aangemaakt en gecorrigeerd

-Added new attributes to classes for compatibility with the simulation. -Expanded the simulation and vehicle functionality -Vehicles now disappear when their position is further than the road length. -Added a few more tests to gtest.
Getting ready to go to system 2.1
